OL,3,CFirst minister apologises to victim of
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs in Scotland
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Scotland
OL,7,FCorrespondent Peter Smith and Scotland
OL,8,FProducer Stephanie Docherty
OL,10,FITV News has been following 'Taylor's'
OL,11,Fstory as she campaigns for the
OL,12,FScottish government to acknowledge the
OL,13,Fabuse she suffered by a group of
OL,14,FPakistani men while she was living in
OL,15,Fcare as a teenager, and her calls for
OL,16,Fa full public inquiry into grooming
OL,17,Fgangs in Scotland.
