OL,3,CFirst minister apologises to victim of
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs in Scotland
OL,6,F"It went okay. It's been a lot for me
OL,7,Fto deal with and I've kept quiet for
OL,8,F15 years, but I do feel we are getting
OL,9,Fone wee step closer.
OL,11,F"He said he's seen what happened to me
OL,12,Fand he did apologise.
OL,14,F"I told him it's not an apology I'm
OL,15,Flooking for, I just want to make sure
OL,16,Fthis doesn't happen to any children in
OL,17,Ffuture."
OL,19,FShe is still not happy that Scotland
OL,20,Fhas stopped short of a full inquiry.
