OL,3,CFirst minister apologises to victim of
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs in Scotland
OL,6,F"I told him the organisations doing
OL,7,Fthis review are the same groups that
OL,8,Flet me down.
OL,10,F"And I told him we want it to be led
OL,11,Fby someone independent, just the same
OL,12,Fas happened in England."
OL,14,FTaylor's care files revealed that
OL,15,Fpolice and care staff knew she was at
OL,16,Fheightened risk of sexual
OL,17,Fexploitation, but they decided not to
OL,18,Fspeak to her or ask if she was being
OL,19,Fabused.
