OL,11,FITV News has now seen more evidence of
OL,12,Fthis after accessing the care files of
OL,13,Fanother survivor who came forward
OL,14,Fafter seeing Taylor's story.
OL,16,FWe are calling her 'Amy' and her files
OL,17,Fshow that care staff could clearly see
OL,18,Fsigns that she was being groomed and
OL,19,Fabused by adults while she was a 12-
OL,20,Fyear-old living in care.
