OL,6,FOne entry from 2000 shows care staff
OL,7,Fhave "great concern" she is "being
OL,8,Fexploited by a (redacted) man, whom
OL,9,Fshe claims to be having a relationship
OL,10,Fwith." And that, "they were found in
OL,11,Fbed together at one point, when she
OL,12,Fwas aged 12."
OL,14,FBy the time she is 14, a team of
OL,15,Fsocial workers describe what's
OL,16,Fhappening to her as "prostitution and
OL,17,Fsexual relationships with older men,"
OL,18,Fnoting that she shows signs of "IV
OL,19,Fdrug use" and "may be pregnant".
