OL,3,CFirst minister apologises to victim of
OL,4,Cgrooming gangs in Scotland
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Jenny Gilruth told
OL,7,FITV News she is committed to listening
OL,8,Fto the survivors and will update
OL,9,FParliament again next week.
OL,11,F"It is important that we get this
OL,12,Fright for them, and I am sorry if they
OL,13,Fdo not feel at the current time that
OL,14,Fis what we are undertaking so I will
OL,15,Fcommit to do that and will update
OL,16,FParliament further next week.
OL,18,F"I will listen to them and engage with
OL,19,Fthem directly and will listen to their
OL,20,Fadvice."
